data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS OFFERING $5,000.00 towards BUYERS CONCESSION (Use to Buydown Interest Rate) with Ratified Contract by December 18, 2023.  USDA ELIGIBLE.     Four years young, this immaculate home,  located in charming Meade's Crossing Community features a bright and open concept design, this home boasts four bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. The upper level is home to four bedrooms, including a luxurious Owner's Suite with a generous walk-in closet and a private ensuite bathroom with an extra-wide stall shower. Additionally, you'll find a conveniently located laundry room on the upper level,  a hallway full bathroom, three additional bedrooms, two of which have spacious walk-in closets.  The sellers have recently upgraded the main level with brand new waterproof luxury vinyl plank flooring. As you step into the main level foyer, you'll enter a Great Room/Kitchen featuring an island, a large sink, and high-quality GE stainless steel appliances and beautiful dark cabinets.  Dining area with a generous sized pantry. A short hallway leads to a convenient powder room,  access to the 2-car garage, and a flex room that can be customized to your needs (home office, hobby room, play room, etc...) making it perfect for relaxation and entertaining.  Step outside to the large VINYL-FENCED  yard, ideal for spending quality time with family and friends, as well as your four-legged companions.  The lower level presents a full, unfinished basement with a rough-in for a three-piece bathroom, offering ample space for your creative ideas to transform it into a welcoming living area.  This peaceful and meticulously landscaped community provides an array of amenities, including a community outdoor pool, a fitness center, a clubhouse, walking paths, playgrounds, a dog park, volleyball and basketball courts, and access to a community garden plot.  Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and Route 140, don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home just in time for the holidays. Schedule your tour today and experience the warmth and comfort this home has to offer!
